'''第42届[[国际象棋奥林匹克|国际象棋奥林匹克]]'''是由[[世界国际象棋联合会|世界国际象棋联合会]]主办的[[国际象棋|国际象棋]]赛事，于2016年9月1日至14日在[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]首都[[巴库|巴库]]举行，这也是阿塞拜疆历史上首次主办该项赛事。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chessdom.com/chess-olympiad-2016-in-baku/ |title=Chess Olympiad 2016 in Baku |publisher=Chessdom |date=8 September 2012 |accessdate=24 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705142300/http://www.chessdom.com/chess-olympiad-2016-in-baku/ |archive-date=2014-07-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

共有1587位棋手参与了本届国际象棋奥林匹克，其中包括894位男棋手与693位女棋手。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://en.chessbase.com/post/2016-baku-rd1-bulgaria-held-to-draw-by-sudan |title=2016 Baku Rd1: Bulgaria held to draw by Sudan |author=Albert Silver |publisher=[[ChessBase|ChessBase]] |date=2 September 2016 |access-date=2016-11-18 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118174130/https://en.chessbase.com/post/2016-baku-rd1-bulgaria-held-to-draw-by-sudan |dead-url=no }}</ref>公开组共有来自175个国家的180支队伍参与，女子组则有来自138个国家的142支队伍参与。其中，[[厄立特里亚|厄立特里亚]]、[[科索沃|科索沃]]与[[南苏丹|南苏丹]]都是首次参加此项赛事。

最终，美国队与中国队分别在公开组与女子组比赛中折桂。乌克兰棋手[[安德烈·沃洛基廷|安德烈·沃洛基廷]]与俄罗斯棋手[[瓦莲京娜·古尼娜|瓦莲京娜·古尼娜]]则分别是两个组别中表现最出色的棋手。<ref name="chess.com-final">{{cite web |url=https://www.chess.com/news/usa-wins-first-olympic-gold-in-40-years-china-clinches-women-section-6522 |title=USA Wins 1st Olympic Gold In 40 Years; China Takes Women's Section |author=Peter Doggers |publisher=[[Chess.com|Chess.com]] |date=13 September 2016 |access-date=2016-11-18 |archive-date=2016-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924155627/https://www.chess.com/news/usa-wins-first-olympic-gold-in-40-years-china-clinches-women-section-6522 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

